<b>A little technical detail - </b>9/6/01 11:33:51 AM<br>~ <b>SourT</b><blockquote>This song - like some other targeted AoE songs- will do damage to everything AROUND the target but not the target itself.  If you want to cast it while in melee range target yourself before singing.  If you want to cast it to help your tank - target the tank then cast it.  If you want to cast it while kiting - aggro some nearby greanie mob and target on him once you have both mobs chasing after you.</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
<b>Song range/effect - </b>8/22/01 4:10:04 PM<br>~ <b>Kocho Divah</b><blockquote>This is one of the few songs that is targetable area effect. If you are standing within melee range of a mob, you will get nuked too. Just back away to a safe distance, let off your moan, then only the mob will be hit (and not your party members).<br><br>Just like other classes can nuke/root themselves accidentally, but not accidentally do this to their groupmates, that is how this song behaves.<br><br>At level 54, I can do 423 damage to all mobs within range. I think I have to update/fix the song formula for this song, hehe.</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
